abstract: Egypt’s security forces raid Cairo house and kill nine Muslim Brotherhood members who Interior Ministry says participated in July bombing of Italian Consulate in Cairo; Islamic State group claims responsibility for attack and human rights advocates criticize Egypt for unfairly targeting Brotherhood.
lead_paragraph: Security forces killed members who the Interior Ministry said had taken part in a bombing at the Italian Consulate in Cairo in July.

headline.print_headline: Middle East; Egypt: Security Forces Kill 9 Brotherhood Members
